message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE. The paper discusses the construction of a dataset for testing common sense reasoning in natural language processing, which falls under the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The dataset also involves video descriptions, which could potentially fall under computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE).
